	(text "KiCad 8-Layer Stackup:\nF.Cu    - TOP: Components, ANALOG routes to jacks, ground fill\nIn1.Cu  - GND: Solid ground plane\nIn2.Cu  - SIG1: TDM/high-speed digital, ground fill\nIn3.Cu  - GND: Solid ground plane (isolation!)\nIn4.Cu  - SIG2: More TDM/digital signals, ground fill\nIn5.Cu  - PWR: Power planes (3.3V/5V)\nIn6.Cu  - GND: Solid ground plane\nB.Cu    - BOTTOM: Components, ANALOG routes to jacks, ground fill"
